    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 18th level, your Radiant chakra is able to cut the bonds holding reality, smaller than the eye can see. Hostile creatures within 60ft of you have their combat capabilities reduced by their ranks of Weakaned.</p><ul><li>1 Rank: The affected creature cannot benefit from the dash action nor from bonuses to speed from jutsu.</li><li>3 Ranks: The affected creature has disadvantage on cosntitution saving throws.</li><li>5 Ranks: The creature must choose between taking an action, bonus action, or moving on its turn.</li></ul><p></p>",
